/span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">,</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">고</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">,</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">대학</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">(</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">원</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">))</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">을 외국에서 이수하고 학사</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">(</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">석사</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">) </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">학위를 취득한 외국인</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">(</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">본인만 외국인</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">)</span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 동국체; font-size: 14.6667px;\">   </span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">✵ </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">국내</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\"